Monday, September 23, 2019

A Favor

   [FrontCover_B1503_ReturningtoTemecula.jpg]
   [B1472_TQCQuirkyLittleQuilts_WEB.jpg]
   My new book Returning to Temecula was introduced 2 months
    ago and Quirky Little Quilts has been available for one year.
   I am so happy with the way they both turned out and I hope you are
   enjoying them as well. I have a little favor to ask, reviews on
   Amazon and Martingale are very helpful and if you would like
   to write a review you can do so using the following links.
   Returning to Temecula - Amazon | Martingale
   Quirky Little Quilts - Amazon | Martingale
   [IMG-0553.jpg]
   If you would like to purchase one or both books you can order
   them here. Order a copy of either book this week and we
     will include a little extra goodie to show our appreciation.
